'''Titanite''' was a rare substance found exclusively on the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Haariden]]. It was the source of the civil war that raged for years on the planet, mostly because of the difficulty and costliness of [[Mining/Legends|mining]] it. It had properties that were used in the production of [[Bacta/Legends|bacta]]. [[Granta Omega]] planned to use this, as well as the [[Alazhi/Legends|alazhi]] of his property on [[Thyferra/Legends|Thyferra]], to dominate [[The galaxy/Legends|the galactic]] bacta market. He used the fighting on Haariden to prevent [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] scientists from gathering all the data on the titanite deposits, however, his plans were disrupted by [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] and [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]].

